OL,3,CSmethwick hospital says sorry to
OL,4,Cpatients amid racism and safety claims
OL,6,FSandwell and West Birmingham NHS Trust
OL,7,Fhas apologised to patients for 'not
OL,8,Freaching the standards of care they
OL,9,Fhave the right to respect.'
OL,11,FIt also says it is appalled by the
OL,12,Faccounts of racism and discrimination
OL,13,Fwhich have been laid bare in Baroness
OL,14,FAmos's report.
OL,16,FThat report was published this
OL,17,Fmorning, with a 23 page review just of
OL,18,FSandwell and West Birmingham NHS trust.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
