CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782892079
OL,3,CSmethwick hospital says sorry to
OL,4,Cpatients amid racism and safety claims
OL,6,FIt concluded that the Baroness is
OL,7,F'concerned about safety for women,
OL,8,Fbirthing people and babies' and laid
OL,9,Fbare racism, experienced by both of
OL,10,Fpatients and staff members.
OL,12,FThe Trust have responded with an open
OL,13,Fletter to the local community in which
OL,14,Fthey said 'we want to begin by saying
OL,15,Fwe are deeply sorry.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
