CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782892079
OL,3,CSmethwick hospital says sorry to
OL,4,Cpatients amid racism and safety claims
OL,6,FThe letter, signed by the Trust's
OL,7,FGroup Chief Executive, Diane Wake,
OL,8,Fsays that 'serving a diverse community
OL,9,Fis a privilege, and we know that we
OL,10,Fmust do more to ensure that every
OL,11,Fperson receives safe, respectful, and
OL,12,Fequitable care.'
OL,14,FThe Trust provides services to more
OL,15,FAsian and Black mothers, alongside a
OL,16,Fwide range of other backgrounds,
OL,17,Fcultures, and ethnicities, compared to
OL,18,Fthe national average.
OL,20,FThe letter lists a range of changes
OL,21,Fthat the Trust has introduced:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
