CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782892079
OL,3,CSmethwick hospital says sorry to
OL,4,Cpatients amid racism and safety claims
OL,6,FThe Trust also says that they will
OL,7,Ftake time to reflect on the eight
OL,8,Frecommendations Baroness Amos made in
OL,9,Fher national review.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/4
